<Layout title="AI Search Agencies Compared - UK 2026 | Rank4AI" description="What each UK AI search agency offers and what they do not. Honest comparison of capabilities, gaps, and best fit for different business needs.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Research', href: '/research/' },
      { label: 'Rankings', href: '/research/rankings/' },
      { label: 'Ai Search Agencies Compared' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Rankings</p>
    <h1 class="mb-4">AI Search Agencies Compared - UK 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on public information, published methodologies, and client outcomes</p>

    <img src="/images/content/stat-77-percent.svg" alt="UK AI visibility research data" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Every agency on this page has genuine AI search capability. But none of them do exactly the same thing. This page is not a ranking. It is a comparison of what each agency offers, what they do not offer, and what type of business they suit best.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Compared on: dedicated AI methodology vs bolted-on SEO, number of platforms tested, ecosystem vs site-only approach, published research, pricing transparency, and UK market focus.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Rank4AI -->
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Rank4AI</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-accent bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">AI Search Specialist</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Works exclusively on AI search visibility. Does not offer traditional SEO, PPC, social media, or web design. Every engagement is about getting businesses recommended by AI platforms. Five Signal Model framework. Tests all six major AI platforms. Ecosystem approach covering site signals, third-party signals, and content architecture. 1,400+ UK business audits completed. Colchester, Essex.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> AI search audits, ongoing AI visibility services, ecosystem strategy, Five Signal Model implementation, multi-platform testing, competitor analysis</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> Traditional SEO, PPC, social media management, web design, Google Ads</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> From GBP 800/mo. Free initial audit available.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">rank4ai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- AwarenessAI -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">AwarenessAI</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">AI Visibility Platform</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Product-led AI visibility business. The core offering is a monitoring dashboard that tracks how AI platforms mention your brand. Agency services are layered on top for businesses that want strategy and implementation support. "6 Pillars" framework. Snapshot and Advanced audit tiers. Ongoing monitoring as a SaaS product.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> AI visibility monitoring dashboard, Snapshot Audit, Advanced Audit, ongoing brand tracking, sentiment monitoring, 6 Pillars framework</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> Traditional SEO, PPC, content creation, web development, full-service digital marketing</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Monitoring from GBP 100/mo. Audit pricing on request.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">awarenessai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Found -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Found</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Digital Marketing Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">"AI-first Everysearch agency" that covers traditional search, AI search, and paid media. Proprietary Luminr technology maps visibility across platforms. Works on llms.txt, schema, metadata for AI. Large agency with the resources for complex multi-channel strategies. London based with an established client portfolio.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> AI search strategy, Luminr visibility mapping, llms.txt implementation, schema optimisation, traditional SEO, paid media, full-service digital marketing</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> Dedicated AI-only service (AI search is part of a broader offering). May not suit businesses wanting a lean, focused engagement.</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Not publicly listed. Enterprise-level engagements.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">found.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Varn -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Varn</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SEO + GEO Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Specialist SEO and data analytics agency with 15+ years experience. Google Premier Partner. AI Visibility Framework as a dedicated practice alongside traditional SEO. Innovation team researching GEO approaches. Particularly strong in healthcare, pharmaceutical, and regulated sectors where trust and compliance are critical.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> AI Visibility Framework, traditional SEO, data analytics, GEO strategy, technical SEO, content strategy for AI, healthcare sector specialism</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> Pure AI-only engagements (SEO is still central). Not suited for businesses wanting to separate AI search from traditional SEO.</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Not publicly listed.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">varn.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Buried Agency -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Buried Agency</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">GEO + SEO Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Bristol-based agency focused on organic search with GEO as a primary service. Entity clarity approach - making sure AI models can clearly identify what your business does. Published thought leadership on GEO. Smaller, focused team. Good for businesses that want hands-on attention from a lean agency rather than being one account among many.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> GEO strategy, entity clarity optimisation, content architecture for AI, structured data, organic search, SEO</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> AI monitoring dashboard, multi-platform tracking tools, PPC, social media, full-service digital. Platform coverage not specified publicly.</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Not publicly listed.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">buriedagency.com</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Hallam -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Hallam</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">B2B Marketing Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Employee-owned, B Corp certified marketing agency. Won The Drum Grand Prix. "Be chosen before the search begins" positioning aligns naturally with AI search, where recommendations happen before a user sees a traditional results page. Adding AI search capability to established B2B marketing services. Nottingham based with strong regional presence.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> B2B marketing strategy, SEO, content marketing, paid media, AI search as emerging service, brand positioning</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> Dedicated AI search methodology (still developing). AI search is part of broader marketing, not a standalone specialism yet.</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Not publicly listed. B2B retainer model.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">hallam.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- CEEK -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">CEEK</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Digital Marketing Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">London, Brighton, and Manchester agency positioning AI search as part of omnichannel strategy. Shopify Partner. Premium brand clients including The Savoy. Their AI search work sits within broader digital marketing, which suits brands that want everything managed together. Strong on e-commerce, particularly Shopify stores.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> Omnichannel digital marketing, AI search as part of SEO, Shopify optimisation, social media, influencer marketing, premium brand positioning</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> Dedicated AI search methodology. AI search is integrated into broader services, not a standalone specialism. Platform coverage not specified.</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Not publicly listed. Premium brand positioning suggests higher-end pricing.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">ceek.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Screaming Frog -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">Screaming Frog</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SEO Agency + Tool Maker</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Creators of the SEO Spider crawler tool used across the industry. Their agency side offers AI Search Optimisation as a dedicated service. Unmatched technical credibility when it comes to crawling, indexing, structured data, and site architecture. Day-rate pricing makes them a good option for focused technical projects rather than ongoing retainers. Henley-on-Thames based.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Offers:</span> AI Search Optimisation service, technical SEO audit, structured data implementation, site architecture review, crawlability analysis, day-rate projects</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Does not offer:</span> Ongoing AI visibility monitoring, content strategy, full-service marketing, retainer-based AI search services. Best for technical projects, not long-term management.</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Day-rate model. Rates not publicly listed.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">screamingfrog.co.uk</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl border border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-lg mb-3">How This Comparison Was Compiled</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">This comparison is based on publicly available information: published service pages, methodology documentation, case studies, blog content, conference presentations, and pricing where available. We contacted agencies for clarification where public information was ambiguous.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Rank4AI is included in this comparison. We believe honest inclusion is more credible than exclusion. We have tried to be equally fair in describing what each agency offers and does not offer, including ourselves.</p>
    </div>
  </div>


    <!-- Internal links -->
