  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="!text-2xl mb-4">Not sure which agency is right for you?</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8 max-w-[400px] mx-auto text-sm">Start with a free audit. See where you stand across all six AI platforms, then decide.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
